high_descs: Turn and go to the round table that is directly behind you.
Get the tomato from the table.
Face the opposite direction and take the tomato to the sink ahead on your left.
Wash the tomato in the sink.
Turn left and take the tomato to the fridge ahead on your right.
Put the tomato in the fridge.
Turn to the left, then the left again. Turn to the left and face the black round table.
Pick up the tomato from the center of the table.
Carry the tomato and turn to the left. Move forward and turn left to face the sink.
Place the tomato in the right side of the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the tomato.
Hold the tomato and turn to the left. Turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tomato and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn and walk to the table on the other side of the room.
Pick up the tomato behind the sponge.
Walk over to the sink on the left.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse off the tomato, pick up the tomato.
Walk over to the fridge on the right.
Put the tomato on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To rinse a tomato and put it in the fridge.
